{"tid":231497,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"創科行業急請人","createTime":"2017-05-06T05:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T16:18:28.000Z","uid":70485,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1212e654614334bef6c180a049b6b79a1d969b1","tid":231497,"uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"節錄於:<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/75802/%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E6%80%A5%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB-%E6%B1%82%E8%81%B7%E8%80%85%E8%96%AA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B%E8%90%BD%E5%B7%AE%E5%A4%A7-%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F75802%2F%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2583%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2596%25AA%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2gKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=3ce8f50c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/75802/%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E6%80%A5%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB-%E6%B1%82%E8%81%B7%E8%80%85%E8%96%AA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B%E8%90%BD%E5%B7%AE%E5%A4%A7-%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83</a><br />\n<br />\n創科行業急請人　僱主、求職者薪金期望落差大　相差五千元<br />\n<br />\n隨着創新及科技行業急速發展，業界求才若渴。數碼港今日(4日)舉行招聘博覽，提供逾500個職位空缺，有僱主指IT行業難請人，期望能以月薪<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一萬二千元</span>聘請到程式編寫員，惟與求職者期望的月薪一萬七千元有明顯落差。<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-n3uqeU_kDJw/WLzix46b3PI/AAAAAAABHBg/s3jyoteonjI06OxtO0gkTC2EaVmzDlFfQCPcB/s640/5764bd57a94c083a9a2f5cadc9ea3878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-n3uqeU_kDJw%2FWLzix46b3PI%2FAAAAAAABHBg%2Fs3jyoteonjI06OxtO0gkTC2EaVmzDlFfQCPcB%2Fs640%2F5764bd57a94c083a9a2f5cadc9ea3878.jpg&h=eda3a8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n顏同學（左一）表示，希望找到一份月薪萬七元左右的工作。（蔡翠嫻攝）<br />\n<br />\n首次參與招聘博覽的互動金融科技行政總裁黃愛玲表示，創科行業一直供大於求，很難聘請到IT人才，公司將根據大學畢業生平均月薪為參考，希望用「Fair Price」月薪萬二元聘請程式編寫員。她寄語大學生不要過份在意起薪點，而是注重向上流動機會，指自己當初亦「升得很快」。<br />\n不過，僱主與求職者的薪金期望有明顯落差。今年就讀理大IT四年級的顏同學指，他期望找到一份人工約萬七元的程式編寫員工作，指自己已做資料搜集，認為該行前景好、向上流動機會大；但假如升遷制度好，薪金低一點也可接受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-1DuLoR0MuHk/WLzkjp1GW2I/AAAAAAABHB0/Si9mIU6C5f8LaJQeRXRSKjO4bw6JwK9CgCLcB/s640/fe334becaa1e90dd57928c888b0b89ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-1DuLoR0MuHk%2FWLzkjp1GW2I%2FAAAAAAABHB0%2FSi9mIU6C5f8LaJQeRXRSKjO4bw6JwK9CgCLcB%2Fs640%2Ffe334becaa1e90dd57928c888b0b89ff.jpg&h=58bc5f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時就讀科大BBA三年級的邱同學和余同學則指，希望到創科公司實習和兼職，會主攻市場推廣職位。她們均指，不會計較薪金高低，主要想累積工作經驗、趁機學習IT知識，為踏出社會早作準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就讀科大BBA的余同學（左）和邱同學（右）希望找到實習和兼職機會，為日後工作做準備。"},{"pid":"a9ab5ba50534a17a619a851115632861919fe9eb","tid":231497,"uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-882GagfniDo/WLzmZZqhToI/AAAAAAABHCE/mpkZhv1nUjgZnatxnHyE3unpPMZ-mLoSwCPcB/s640/Image%2B002.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-882GagfniDo%2FWLzmZZqhToI%2FAAAAAAABHCE%2FmpkZhv1nUjgZnatxnHyE3unpPMZ-mLoSwCPcB%2Fs640%2FImage%252B002.png&h=bb6b6100&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e852d74c9bcd2c8a8a6a7ffee5d757d5c9a33efb","tid":231497,"uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-0fntDkldyvs/WLzmZbV8QvI/AAAAAAABHCI/XBVPNFjSvZAfVX4XSda9Y_b4VR_hEpLrwCPcB/s640/Image%2B003.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-0fntDkldyvs%2FWLzmZbV8QvI%2FAAAAAAABHCI%2FXBVPNFjSvZAfVX4XSda9Y_b4VR_hEpLrwCPcB%2Fs640%2FImage%252B003.png&h=7ddc0476&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f04443f38be9a1